{"tid":2349613,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"不理性講句，香港樂壇唔值得擁有林家謙","createTime":"2021-01-01T16:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T16:50:25.000Z","uid":37977,"like":27,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a374d867f5c4ee2536b55a29565d95d50a51030a","tid":2349613,"uid":37977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:19:49.000Z","msg":"家謙嘅才華大家有目共睹，但係連十大都入唔到一首<br />\n你哋仲可以話香港樂壇未死？<br />\n我知各花入各眼，我好中意karen、馮允謙佢地，輸唔係問題，但連家謙一首live都聽唔到，個人覺得真係好撚唔合理<br />\n最喜愛男歌手係姜濤，ok大家有唔同口味有唔同偶像<br />\n但最喜愛歌曲係姜濤我真係呆左，一人之境輸係輸在首歌定係輸在個人，大家各自有定論啦<br />\n恭喜姜濤，希望你頂得住啲輿論<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee85addc9a5e528fe96e42aac7cf532dd6ba30a8","tid":2349613,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:21:21.000Z","msg":"坤哥拎完越嚟越受歡迎<br />\n你少擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d348c76d1055c0281f85226de00373de2466d2","tid":2349613,"uid":366018,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:23:35.000Z","msg":"真 完全唔明點解一人之境會入唔到十大 痴撚線"},{"pid":"b67028ab8eb354110a9739c3881597c23fc928af","tid":2349613,"uid":36894,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:27:57.000Z","msg":"出道第二年有男銅喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9c4716bd58f09191d2c041c2f64d58794244df","tid":2349613,"uid":218166,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:28:31.000Z","msg":"要屌就屌班DJ啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef6097a3a62b25593797de0672c52460a292e3c","tid":2349613,"uid":237415,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:29:23.000Z","msg":"姜啲fans咁撚黐線 <br />\n入唔到最喜愛歌手同埋歌曲就假<br />\n反而冇十大真係癡撚線"},{"pid":"141526f1fdbd85876a739a930bb7c1b7354f1c6d","tid":2349613,"uid":39287,"l